\
\ Test de FGDRIVER
\
EXIST? RAND NOT ?\ INCLUDE ..\TFCLUB\RANDOM.FTH
EXIST? FASTGRAF NOT ?\ INCLUDE FGDRIVER.FTH

ONLY FORTH ALSO FASTGRAF ALSO
FORTH DEFINITIONS
DECIMAL

200 CONSTANT RECTANGLES

VARIABLE OLDMODE
VARIABLE MINX
VARIABLE MAXX
VARIABLE MINY
VARIABLE MAXY
VARIABLE XRES
VARIABLE YRES

: FGDEMO23 ( --- )
   FASTGRAPH?
   IF
      FGGETMODE OLDMODE !
      FGAUTOMODE FGSETMODE
      3 3 FGBOXDEPTH
      FGGETMAXX 1+ XRES !
      FGGETMAXY 1+ YRES !
      RECTANGLES 0
      DO
         RAND XRES @ MOD MINX !
         RAND XRES @ MOD MAXX !
         RAND YRES @ MOD MINY !
         RAND YRES @ MOD MAXY !
         RAND 16 MOD FGSETCOLOR
         MINX @ MAXX @ 2DUP >
         IF
            SWAP
         THEN
         MINY @ MAXY @ 2DUP >
         IF
            SWAP
         THEN
         FGBOX
      LOOP
      " D‚monstration de FastGraph (Appuyez sur une touche)" FGTEXT
      FGWAITKEY
      OLDMODE @ FGSETMODE
      FGRESET
      1 FGCURSOR
   ELSE
      CR ." Le driver FastGraph n'est pas charg‚ !!" CR
   THEN
;

EOF

